    <h2 class="content-subhead">Horizontal Menu</h2>
    <p>
        Create horizontal menus by adding the {{code "yui3-menu-horizontal"}} class name. You can mark the active list element by adding the {{code "yui3-menu-active"}} class to the list element.
    </p>

    {{> lists/horizontal}}

