    <p>
        You can add disabled links to your menu by adding an {{code "<a>"}} element with the {{code "yui3-menu-disabled"}} class name. Disabled items do not inherit hover styles, and appear faded. 
    </p>

    {{> lists/disabled}}

  {{#code}}
    {{> lists/disabled}}
  {{/code}}


    <h2 class="content-subhead">Paginators</h2>
    <p>
        Paginators are list-based elements too! You can implement a paginator control by adding the {{code "yui3-paginator"}} classname to a {{code "<ul>"}} element. Paginator controls generally look like buttons, but omit the {{code "yui3-button"}} class name if you want simple paginators.
    </p>

    {{> lists/paginator}}

